MERGE [ProductCategory] USING (
VALUES (@p0, @p1, @p2, @p3, @p4, @p5, @p6, @p7, @p8, @p9, @p10, @p11, @p12, @p13, 0),
(@p14, @p15, @p16, @p17, @p18, @p19, @p20, @p21, @p22, @p23, @p24, @p25, @p26, @p27, 1),
(@p28, @p29, @p30, @p31, @p32, @p33, @p34, @p35, @p36, @p37, @p38, @p39, @p40, @p41, 2),
(@p42, @p43, @p44, @p45, @p46, @p47, @p48, @p49, @p50, @p51, @p52, @p53, @p54, @p55, 3)) AS i ([DateCreated], [DateModified], [Description], [HomeFlag], [HomeOrder], [Image], [Name], [ParentId], [SeoAlias], [SeoDescription], [SeoKeywords], [SeoPageTitle], [SortOrder], [Status], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([DateCreated], [DateModified], [Description], [HomeFlag], [HomeOrder], [Image], [Name], [ParentId], [SeoAlias], [SeoDescription], [SeoKeywords], [SeoPageTitle], [SortOrder], [Status])
VALUES (i.[DateCreated], i.[DateModified], i.[Description], i.[HomeFlag], i.[HomeOrder], i.[Image], i.[Name], i.[ParentId], i.[SeoAlias], i.[SeoDescription], i.[SeoKeywords], i.[SeoPageTitle], i.[SortOrder], i.[Status])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted0;

SELECT [t].[Id] FROM [ProductCategory] t
